OL,6,FThe Troubles, Covid-19, Northern
OL,7,FIreland's licensing laws, lack of
OL,8,Fpublic transport and taxi
OL,9,Finfrastructure, revellers' personal
OL,10,Fsafety, a problematic drugs scene, and
OL,11,Fthe lack of a central body responsible
OL,12,Ffor nightlife - all play their part in
OL,13,Fholding Belfast back.
OL,15,FThe Consumer Council has researched
OL,16,Fnight time travel and how safe people
OL,17,Ffeel. The findings are stark.
