OL,6,FA total of 68% of respondents said
OL,7,Fthat personal safety travelling at
OL,8,Fnight and their concerns for their
OL,9,Fpersonal safety actually deterred them
OL,10,Ffrom travelling at least some of the
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FThat rose to 75% of people with a
OL,14,Fdisability and 80% of female consumers.
OL,16,FConsequently, Alison examines the
OL,17,Freasons behind the shortage of taxi
OL,18,Fdrivers post pandemic, and speaks to
OL,19,FTranslink chief executive Chris Conway
OL,20,Fabout a year round late night bus
OL,21,Fservice.
