OL,3,CBelfast's nightlife in the spotlight
OL,4,Cin the next UTV Up Close
OL,6,FBar owner of over 50 years Willie
OL,7,FJack, MBE says the city needs a night
OL,8,Ftime Czar to co-ordinate all the
OL,9,Fservices required to make the city
OL,10,Fmore vibrant: "We need to get a big
OL,11,Fpersonality... we need a manager.
OL,12,FLet's make the city safe. That's the
OL,13,Fbiggest single thing we can do. Get
OL,14,Feverybody into town and get them out
OL,15,Fsafely."
OL,17,FAmy Lame, London's night time Czar,
OL,18,Fagrees and points out that Belfast and
OL,19,FLondon share the same challenges and
OL,20,Fopportunities.
