OL,4,Cin the next UTV Up Close
OL,6,FShe feels that Belfast would benefit
OL,7,Ffrom a Czar.
OL,9,F"You've got an incredibly rich history
OL,10,Fthat should be preserved and also
OL,11,Fbuilt, built upon. So I think the
OL,12,Fnights Czar or night-time advisor
OL,13,Fcould really help make that happen."
OL,15,FAlison also asks, "Is 'going out
OL,16,Fearly' the new 'staying out late'?"
OL,18,FShe looks at this growing trend and
OL,19,Fhow local venues are responding to the
OL,20,Fshift in demand.
