OL,3,CBelfast's nightlife in the spotlight
OL,4,Cin the next UTV Up Close
OL,6,FShe talks to Joe Dougan of the
OL,7,FLimelight about an over-30s event
OL,8,Frunning from 5pm to 9pm which sold out
OL,9,Fin just five minutes.
OL,11,FColin Neill, Hospitality Ulster
OL,12,Fbelieves the answer lies in
OL,13,Fcapitalising on our unique pub culture
OL,14,Fand not to try to replicate what goes
OL,15,Fon in other cities.
OL,17,F"We're not Brazil, we're Northern
OL,18,FIreland. Let's not copy other people,
OL,19,Flet's build a unique product. We
OL,20,Falready have the foundations." he says.
